--------------------------------------------------------------------------
To execute BTDroidserver

./BTDroidserver

or

python BTDroidServer
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
dependences
pyhton,python-bluetooth,xdotool,bluez

sudo apt-get install python-bluetooth xdotool
